sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VLLM as vLLM Container<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant GPU as AMD GPU<br/>(ROCm/HIP)
    participant S3 as S3/Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TGIS as vLLM TGIS Adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant MMRouter as ModelMesh Router

    Note over VLLM,S3: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup
    VLLM->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / HMAC
    S3-->>VLLM: Model artifacts
    VLLM->>GPU: Load model to GPU memory<br/>PCIe/Infinity Fabric

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (RHOAI 3.x - HTTP)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    KRBP->>VLLM: Proxied request<br/>HTTP/8000, plaintext (localhost)<br/>Auth: None (proxied)
    VLLM->>GPU: Inference computation<br/>ROCm/HIP memory
    GPU-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
    VLLM-->>KRBP: JSON Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Encrypted response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over MMRouter,GPU: Flow 3: TGIS gRPC Inference (ModelMesh)
    MMRouter->>TGIS: gRPC GenerateRequest<br/>gRPC/8033, mTLS<br/>Auth: Client cert
    TGIS->>VLLM: In-process Python call
    VLLM->>GPU: Inference computation
    GPU-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
    VLLM-->>TGIS: Generated text
    TGIS-->>MMRouter: gRPC GenerateResponse<br/>mTLS
